directions: ["Blend with spoon and shape with butter on top.", "Bake until done."]

title: Chicken Divan
ingredients: ["1 pkg. frozen broccoli, cooked and drained", "3 boiled chicken breasts, cubed", "1/2 c. grated Cheddar cheese", "1 can cream of chicken soup", "1/2 c. Hellmann's mayonnaise", "bread crumbs"]
directions: ["In casserole place cooked broccoli, then chicken.", "In separate bowl mix together soup, mayonnaise and cheese.", "Spread over chicken.", "Sprinkle bread crumbs over top of mixture.", "Bake at 350\u00b0 for 30 minutes or until bubbles around edge."]
NER: ["cream of chicken soup", "chicken breasts", "cheddar cheese", "mayonnaise", "frozen broccoli", "bread crumbs"]

title: Rice Pudding
ingredients: ["3 qt. milk", "9 Tbsp. rice", "2 1/4 c. sugar", "1/4 tsp. salt"]
directions: ["Combine and bring to a slight boil.", "Place in oven at 300\u00b0 or 325\u00b0.", "When skim forms on top, stir it down.", "Continue until desired thickness."]
